					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fridakahlo.org/self-portrait-dedicated-to-dr-eloesser.jsp&quot;&gt;Self Portrait Dedicated to Dr Eloesser&lt;/a&gt;, 1940." created="Fri, 22 Apr 2022 15:58:46 GMT" inlineImage="http://scripting.com/images/2022/04/22/kahloSelfPortrait.png"/>
