			<outline text="April 21" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:38:47 GMT" type="calendarDay" name="21">
				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1517240478386855938&quot;&gt;Poll&lt;/a&gt;: Have you had Covid?" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 20:35:03 GMT" type="outline" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1517240478386855938"/>
				<outline text="I can’t believe &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/by/alexander-burns&quot;&gt;reporters&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/by/jonathan-martin&quot;&gt;keep&lt;/a&gt; holding &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ifindkarma/status/1517322258091413504&quot;&gt;material evidence&lt;/a&gt; secret to promote their &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.target.com/p/this-will-not-pass-by-jonathan-martin-alexander-burns-hardcover/-/A-85279499?ref=tgt_adv_XS000000&amp;AFID=google_pla_df&amp;fndsrc=tgtao&amp;DFA=71700000012510700&amp;CPNG=PLA_Entertainment%2BShopping%7CEntertainment_Ecomm_Hardlines&amp;adgroup=SC_Entertainment&amp;LID=700000001170770pgs&amp;LNM=PRODUCT_GROUP&amp;network=g&amp;device=c&amp;location=1023511&amp;targetid=pla-308131048976&amp;ds_rl=1246978&amp;ds_rl=1248099&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwgYSTBhDKARIsAB8KuktXDJt_Ygr674oRHHR_ef2Aqk5ePexrb0dpzGlWmSMDzbKaadT63ecaAvgCEALw_wcB&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds&quot;&gt;books&lt;/a&gt;. And other reporters let them slide. With &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/AdamParkhomenko/status/1517315115028201473&quot;&gt;glee&lt;/a&gt;. What a racket. " created="Fri, 22 Apr 2022 02:11:16 GMT" type="outline" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1517329145323261953"/>
				<outline text="We should just discount the president's approval rating down to zero and then we could view 39% as a historic high. But seriously folks, the president's approval rating is just how the news, as it's reported, bounces off the minds of the people the pollsters talk to. You could model it like they model weather reports, and tune up the news coverage to create any approval rating you want." created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 15:12:21 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="A new season of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hbo.com/gentleman-jack&quot;&gt;Gentleman Jack&lt;/a&gt; is coming to HBO later this month. Great show. " created="Fri, 22 Apr 2022 02:22:20 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="After reading this &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Full_stop&quot;&gt;Wikipedia article&lt;/a&gt; I still don’t understand what “full stop” means. Instead of saying “full stop” couldn’t you just stop?" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:45:30 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="I’m a lifetime Knicks fan, rooting for the Celtics proving life is weird." created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:58:04 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="It'll be interesting to see if any fans show up in Brooklyn to support the Nets." created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:41:53 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="The big problem isn't climate change, it's getting people to work together instead of just working for themselves. And to start working together we have to learn how to listen. It's hard, when we're raised to not listen." created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:41:07 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="I watched a tiny bit of the French presidential debate yesterday and what struck me is how civil they were with each other, compared to US politics." created="Thu, 21 Apr 2022 13:38:48 GMT" type="outline"/>
